Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.43,0:01:22.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比起回忆 还是去追求理想的今天{\fad(0,1025)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好悠闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  之前的战斗仿佛假的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是四魂碎片的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且正在接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:01:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗅到戈薇的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地来见你的  过的还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何指教  瘦皮狼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  不可以一见面就打架喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆  要不是这种情形…\N我马上宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一点都没变  烂狗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次看到你都\N紧张兮兮叽叽呱呱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  跟这种人在一起不累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…\N喂  钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别扯一些没礼貌的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“犬夜叉只是觉得\N戈薇会被抢走而焦急”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你老是这么想\N就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  别跟着起哄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是一刻都不得闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第46话 兽郎丸与影郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你奈落城的所在位置?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的话我们就不会这么累了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那家伙\N在城的周围布满了结界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为同伴报仇的事就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要把双脚的\N四魂之玉碎片交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再乖乖躲回\N巢穴里发抖就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  烂狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你挥刀意外的迟钝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙还是很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  怎么可能突然变轻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种就别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没空在这跟烂狗吵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大烂狗  在我杀了奈落之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇就先让你保管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢动她  我就要你好看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙连逃走的时候\N都自信满满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着发那么大的脾气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候发脾气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很高兴他为我吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就不能用温柔点的方式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有够累人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟…跟我在一起真的那么累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在沮丧什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着在意钢牙说的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他是在意戈薇小姐说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢  钢牙?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟神乐一样…绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖狼族的少主…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你比犬夜叉\N早一步闻到我的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…是奈落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那个叫神乐的女人\N相同的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙就是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴被你杀害的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我要在这讨回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当作我新的分身的饵食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笼子?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  我是不知道你载着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里撞见我是你气数已尽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要报我同伴的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手是这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧  兽郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子怎么搞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先收拾这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再将你们通通解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  奈落!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快拿掉这小子的辔头跟锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付你这样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子动作真快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使受限制了还是比我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股寒气是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子的辔头里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要单独行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明就还不能\N好好的使用铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有恶心的钢牙那家伙的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要收拾奈落的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以让钢牙抢先
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆  我现在忙得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能追上我的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙  原来你在逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于来了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙仇也不报就逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我想象中要识相多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拿我跟那个\N胆小鬼瘦皮狼相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…新的奈落分身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兽郎丸  我就解开你的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你放手一搏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开辔头的兽郎丸谁都挡不住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到把这里所有人杀光为止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的  这个叫兽郎丸的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阴阳怪气的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总归是奈落的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却打掉了\N应该是自己人的奈落的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙敌我不分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才被辔头与锁链封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么轻易就被打中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是陷阱吗?不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子怎么看都不像是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会卖弄小聪明战斗的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一口气解决掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相上下?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手腕变长了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的身体能变化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到奈落了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:09:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你怎么回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是逃回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  是直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且不论奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他带的那个头怪怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发出非常危险的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的直觉绝对不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  凭这一点就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉真是个大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候他肯定是\N被兽郎丸打得哭爹喊娘啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还遇到犬夜叉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  钢牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是我们多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和犬夜叉在一起的戈薇大姐\N不是也危险了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐东西  为什么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该自己发觉到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个浑蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砍断手腕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有砍到的触感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是自行从兽狼丸身上分离
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手腕又接上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个根本不是手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…从地面?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子的内脏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道真是不错  兽郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…居然还有一只
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是影郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沉睡在兽郎丸的肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在兽郎丸的肚子里…那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那辔头是为了封印你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为兽郎丸只服从我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使对像是奈落也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N剩下的人也处理掉吧  兽郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情的吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在吸哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭这种速度也想打倒我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的刀比较恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就躲到被窝里睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你还不能乱动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子已经开了个洞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆  这只是家常便饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人的命  我要了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大烂狗  你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然让戈薇遭受这种危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明就夹着尾巴逃掉还敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只有这次\N才跟你道谢  大混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我刚才的处境十分危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:13:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只怪模怪样的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从兽郎丸的肚子里跑出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从兽郎丸身上感受到的寒气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这家伙的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫影郎丸的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作快到我们追不上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们以为我是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就没有能\N从我脚底下逃走的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有嘴巴厉害而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很敢说嘛!我要把你捏碎!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连嘴皮子也不怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的速度不过如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兽郎丸  你的对手是本大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别丢人现眼了  烂狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连那只笨妖怪都束手无策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!这浑蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是连影郎丸都抓不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拿我和你相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐看得见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他抢在影郎丸的前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你死!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…从土里?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  又潜下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好!脚被封住就没有胜算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉还倒在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该吃那女人的内脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影郎丸  你敢碰戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你连骨头都吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你休想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…是刀变轻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他用单手挥动铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他头脑简单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概脑袋被冲昏  忘记重量了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁头脑简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又潜下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉才是  好严重的伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烂狗  你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙的脚也中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子一点用都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开吧  瘦皮狼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我把兽郎丸砍成两…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变重了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然刚才是因为\N一心要保护戈薇才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会在旁边吠的胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便连你也一起砍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就说声谢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗再拖下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体也会撑不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道潜入地底的\N影郎丸会从哪里袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是至少能封住\N土里的影郎丸的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  锡杖借一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么策略吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种毒…虽然效果不长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要逼出影郎丸应该够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土变红了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点抓住影郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土里的毒应该会让他动作变慢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没出息的烂狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下爬不起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉!你振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别慌张  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我一个人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要没有碍手碍脚的影郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一只白痴妖怪是轻而易举
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩这一只就一口气打倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影郎丸的气息消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是潜到暗处了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋!钢牙  快回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烂狗就躲起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开  钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让开的话\N我就连你一起砍成两半
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才发现太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉身碎骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  害我花了那么多功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:19:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是打算连我一起宰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  我要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全没有半点犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就狠狠的一刀劈过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为他认为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以钢牙的速度一定能够避开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  犬夜叉?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了  罗唆的瘦皮狼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再发牢骚我就真的劈下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好笑  有本事就来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个没死透的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙  今天就先离开好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么啊  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明受了重伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有想过再打下去\N会有什么后果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙  今天真的很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你帮了大忙  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为这样\N钢牙就会乖乖回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:21:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能放心把你\N交给那一无是处的烂狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  居然让他胡言乱语
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你有危险的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会来救你的  再见了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住  臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又把钢牙放走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  犬夜叉的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我会输给那只瘦皮狼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先治疗伤口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说过不用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且刚才那什么态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了讨好那家伙还向他谄媚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是丢人现眼  让人看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那什么眼神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回家去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去啊  我才不会拦你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…话说完了就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要好好帮法师疗伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这样子  真是长不大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:30.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,何不把真正重要的事物以外{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:42.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,全部 都舍弃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:49.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:53.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:58.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:05.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:12.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:19.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:27.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:35.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.02,0:23:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十年前设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.06,0:23:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让犬夜叉和桔梗\N自相残杀的奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又布下了天罗地网\N要除掉桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:23:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己体内残留的\N鬼蜘蛛的心仰慕着桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他似乎很痛恨这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.80,0:24:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.07,0:24:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉不可能置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.30,0:24:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么  犬夜叉?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.04,0:24:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何与桔梗那样抱在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.31,0:24:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落残留的鬼蜘蛛灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.48,0:24:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
